      "title": "US Embassy won\u2019t offer NIV passback services until Monday",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Consular Section of the United States Embassy in Sri Lanka today announced that they will not offer NIV passback services on Friday (26).",
        "However, the Section will offer the service today (24), tomorrow (25), and Monday (29) at 3.30 pm. as usual. Therefore, the embassy requested the public to plan accordingly."
      ],
